<view class="page">
  <view class="top-tip">
    请填写下方申请表
  </view>
  <form class="form" bind:submit="formSubmit">
    <view class="name-container">
      <tesla-input required label="姓氏"></tesla-input>
      <tesla-input required label="名字"></tesla-input>
    </view>
    <tesla-input required label="邮箱"></tesla-input>
    <tesla-input required label="手机号"></tesla-input>
    <picker bindchange="bindProvincePickerChange" value="{{province}}" range="{{provinces}}">
      <tesla-input required label="省份" value="{{provinces[province]}}"></tesla-input>
    </picker>
    <picker bindchange="bindCityPickerChange" value="{{city}}" range="{{cities}}">
      <tesla-input required label="城市" value="{{cities[city]}}"></tesla-input>
    </picker>
    <view class="checkbox-container">
      <label class="checkbox">
        <checkbox color="#000" value="cb" checked="true" /><text>获取 Tesla 最新资讯</text>
      </label>
    </view>
    <view class="bottom-tip">
      为什么试驾要预约？为保证每位客户都享受到一对一的试驾体验，我们需要根据您提供的信息来提前安排合适的试驾地点和时间。如您填写并提交上述信息，表示您同意特斯拉按照客户隐私政策(www.tesla.cn/about/legal)收集、使用这些信息。
    </view>
    <button type="primary" class="submitBtn">预约试驾</button>
  </form>
</view>